<h1>Country tournament</h1><br/>

<p><b>Official Rules for the Team Tournament, European Pinball Championship 2007<br/>
On Saturday June 17st KTH in Stockholm will host the Country Tournament of the European Pinball Championship 2007.</b><br/><br/>

